{"tid":2418543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暴動案被告違宵禁令 未能提供安心出行紀錄遭撤保釋須還柙","createTime":"2021-02-22T16:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T16:34:31.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d7d765da541603109ebc8519bdd7880cf7ccceff","tid":2418543,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:34:31.000Z","msg":"傅於上周六（20日）晚上11時許被警方發現流連於旺角地士道公園內，違反保釋條件中的宵禁令，因而被捕。辯方解釋，傅當晚10時跟兩名友人晚膳後打算回家，但途中到了公園內聊天嬉戲，不知不覺間錯過宵禁時間。<br />\n<br />\n主任裁判官羅德泉又多次問及被告，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">當晚到餐廳用膳時有否實名登記或使用安心出行作紀錄，惟被告未能提供相關資料。羅官因此不接納辯方解釋</span></span></strong>，考慮到被告有機會再犯事，決定撤銷被告保釋，還柙看管至下次提訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/6MAAWUGJJZFLZEVJLSRUZYPGVU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0Y31eECzRIQ8mNkAiGI1sLljphD2b7JkF5mIqU8CZPr2AcYrV2Bdm96ig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2F6MAAWUGJJZFLZEVJLSRUZYPGVU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0Y31eECzRIQ8mNkAiGI1sLljphD2b7JkF5mIqU8CZPr2AcYrV2Bdm96ig&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XrQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=0617fb6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2F6MAAWUGJJZFLZEVJLSRUZYPGVU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0Y31eECzRIQ8mNkAiGI1sLljphD2b7JkF5mIqU8CZPr2AcYrV2Bdm96ig&h=b6bf1f23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/6MAAWUGJJZFLZEVJLSRUZYPGVU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0Y31eECzRIQ8mNkAiGI1sLljphD2b7JkF5mIqU8CZPr2AcYrV2Bdm96ig</a>"}]}